OL,3,CGruelling heat expected to give way to
OL,4,Ccooler temperatures and sporadic rain
OL,6,FThe UK is set to welcome fresher
OL,7,Fconditions on Sunday as baking heat
OL,8,Fgives way to cooler temperatures and
OL,9,Fsporadic rain.
OL,11,FThe Met Office said Saturday marked
OL,12,Fthe end of the sweltering heatwave
OL,13,Fthat has baked the nation for much of
OL,14,Fthis week, with the mercury nearing
OL,15,F30C in south-east England.
OL,17,FOn Sunday, scattered showers are
OL,18,Fexpected across the UK, with
OL,19,Ftemperatures closer to the average for
OL,20,Fthis time of year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
