OL,3,CGruelling heat expected to give way to
OL,4,Ccooler temperatures and sporadic rain
OL,6,FAt least 14 people died during the
OL,7,Fheatwave after getting into
OL,8,Fdifficulties in bodies of water.
OL,10,FOn Saturday, Nottinghamshire Police
OL,11,Fsaid a 19-year-old man had died after
OL,12,Fentering the water at Balderton Lake,
OL,13,Foff Heron Way in New Balderton.
OL,15,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,16,Fscene on Thursday where the man was
OL,17,Frecovered from the water and treated
OL,18,Fat the scene before being taken to
OL,19,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
