OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780251071
OL,3,CGruelling heat expected to give way to
OL,4,Ccooler temperatures and sporadic rain
OL,6,FThe force said the family has been
OL,7,Finformed and were being supported by
OL,8,Fspecialist officers.
OL,10,FThere are not believed to be any
OL,11,Fsuspicious circumstances and a report
OL,12,Fwill be prepared for the coroner,
OL,13,Fpolice said.
OL,15,FIt comes after police said a 15-year-
OL,16,Fold girl had died in hospital on
OL,17,FSaturday after getting into
OL,18,Fdifficulties in the sea off the coast
OL,19,Fof Merseyside on Bank Holiday Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
