OL,3,CGruelling heat expected to give way to
OL,4,Ccooler temperatures and sporadic rain
OL,6,FChiedza Nyanjowa, from Cheshire, was
OL,7,Ftaken to Alder Hey Children's Hospital
OL,8,Fafter swimming at Formby beach,
OL,9,FMerseyside Police said.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the force said the
OL,12,Ffamily would like to express their
OL,13,Fgratitude to people who had helped the
OL,14,Fteenager, who they described as a
OL,15,F"bubbly person" who loved cooking and
OL,16,Fwanted to be a nurse so she could
OL,17,F"give back".
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@OO]yD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
