OL,3,CGruelling heat expected to give way to
OL,4,Ccooler temperatures and sporadic rain
OL,6,FThe hot weather has attracted many
OL,7,Fpeople to open-water swimming,
OL,8,Fresulting in a number of deaths in
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire, West Yorkshire,
OL,10,FCornwall, Hampshire, Warwickshire,
OL,11,FCheshire, Pembrokeshire, Lincolnshire
OL,12,Fand Lancashire over recent days.
OL,14,FThese include a 72-year-old woman who
OL,15,Fdied after being pulled from the water
OL,16,Fat West Angle Bay beach in
OL,17,FPembrokeshire, Wales, on Sunday and a
OL,18,F13-year-old boy, understood to be Reco
OL,19,FPuttock, who died after getting into
OL,20,Fdifficulty at Leadbeater Dam, near
OL,21,FHalifax, West Yorkshire, on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
